{"type": "article", "id": 17646, "title": "树叶灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-17T06:50:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 110, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061531471S30gtAEilqBoOy7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些像树叶一样的灯来自韩国设计工作室 ilsangisang。他们在一些对环境无害的纸张上刷上夜光油墨，分别印刷了银杏叶、悬铃木叶和榆树叶的外形和纹路，在黑暗中发出幽静的绿色的光，非常精细。点上灯时，除了能见到树叶的纹路，还有蝴蝶、蜻蜓、青蛙等昆虫的剪影，让这组灯显得更自然。设计师想要提醒人们珍惜树木这样宝贵的自然资源。<a href=\"http://www.29cm.co.kr/brand/brandshop.asp?idx=760&amp;tabcode=2&amp;sPT=s\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144739iuRCVx9GMkXyJ23P.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144739P9c5XDrTkF2gfBKM.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144740H6qJja1Kg7l2RfTC.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144740VxRiawojuA7qKWNP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144741A25yjYLHgXCfhuti.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144741mCeKOIdjWETHRiwa.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}